      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Stefan Knappe</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:278px;\"><a href=\"http://www.quarkchess.de/belct/body_index.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/9/96/StefanKnappe.jpg\" width=\"276\" height=\"207\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:StefanKnappe.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Stefan Knappe during <a href=\"/BELCT_2001\" title=\"BELCT 2001\">BELCT 2001</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Stefan Knappe</b>,<br />\na German economist, club chess player <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and avocational computer chess programmer. \nHe is author of the chess program <a href=\"/Matador\" title=\"Matador\">Matador</a>, which also participated as <i>Lokalmatador</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> at the <a href=\"/BELCT_2001\" title=\"BELCT 2001\">BELCT 2001</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Berlin\">Berlin</a>. \nAlong with <a href=\"/Dieter_B%C3%BCr%C3%9Fner\" title=\"Dieter Bürßner\">Dieter Bürßner</a> et al., Stefan was member of the <i>ChessCoach - Team</i>, developing chess training software for <a href=\"/index.php?title=Palm&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Palm (page does not exist)\">Palm</a> and <a href=\"/index.php?title=Pocket-PC&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Pocket-PC (page does not exist)\">Pocket-PC</a> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, \nalso affiliated with the <i>Inside Chess</i> project focusing on <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web_development\">web development</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefan_Knappe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=33797\">Quark and Leiden</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Knappe</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, May 18, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/ICT_2001\" title=\"ICT 2001\">ICT 2001</a>, <a href=\"/Quark\" title=\"Quark\">Quark</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=34982\">Futility + WAC</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Knappe</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, November 07, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Futility Pruning</a>, <a href=\"/Win_at_Chess\" title=\"Win at Chess\">Win at Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=43019\">wacnew.epd &amp; single search improvements</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Knappe</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 16, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=43033\">wacnew.epd &amp; single search improvements (nullmove)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Knappe</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 17, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=43060\">wacnew.epd &amp; single search improvements (extensions)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Knappe</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 19, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a>, <a href=\"/Win_at_Chess\" title=\"Win at Chess\">Win at Chess</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=346731\">Testposition of Matador-Alarm CCT6</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Knappe</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 03, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/CCT6\" title=\"CCT6\">CCT6</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=47806&amp;start=1\">Re: Beowulf curve calibration results for depth = 5 plies</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Knappe</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, June 08, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Beowulf\" title=\"Beowulf\">Beowulf</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=1610\">Polyglot &amp; log-file</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Stefan Knappe</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, February 10, 2005</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefan_Knappe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ratings.fide.com/profile/24625450\">FIDE Knappe, Stefan</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://schachbezirk4.de/dwz/player.php?pkz=10108386\">DWZ Bezirk IV Stefan Knappe</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20060402233948/http://www.stefanknappe.de/\">Stefan Knappe's Homepage</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>, April 02, 2006)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20060303085114/http://www.pda-schach.de/\">PDA-Schach, Computerschach-News, Schachprogramme für den PDA</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>, March 03, 2006)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20070106185813/http://www.chesscoach.de/home/index.php\">Schachtraining - Home</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>, January 07, 2007)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20171217230520/http://www.inside-chess.de:80/\">Inside Chess</a> (German) (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>, December 17, 2017)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stefan_Knappe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.quarkchess.de/belct/\">BELCT 2001 Berlin is worth a trip!</a> Photos <a href=\"/BELCT_2001\" title=\"BELCT 2001\">BELCT 2001</a> by <a href=\"/Thomas_Mayer\" title=\"Thomas Mayer\">Thomas Mayer</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20060402233948/http://www.stefanknappe.de/\">Stefan Knappe's Homepage</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>, April 02, 2006)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.wiktionary.org/wiki/Lokalmatador\">Lokalmatador – Wiktionary</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20070107174813/http://www.chesscoach.de/chesscoach-team.html\">ChessCoach - ChessCoach - Team</a> (<a rel=\"